import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-accounts', templateUrl: './accounts.component.html', styleUrls: ['./accounts.component.css'] }) export class AccountsComponent { }

Banking Accounts

Choose from our comprehensive range of banking solutions

Checking Accounts

Essential Checking

  • No minimum balance requirement
  • Free online and mobile banking
  • Complimentary debit card
  • 24/7 ATM access
  • Monthly fee: $0

Premium Checking

  • Preferred interest rates
  • Free checks and money orders
  • Waived ATM fees worldwide
  • Enhanced fraud protection
  • Monthly fee: $25 (waived with $5000+ balance)

Savings Accounts

High-Yield Savings

  • Competitive APY of 3.50%
  • No monthly maintenance fees
  • Mobile check deposit
  • Automatic savings programs
  • Minimum opening deposit: $100

Premium Savings

  • Premium APY of 4.00%
  • Priority customer service
  • Free wire transfers
  • Exclusive financial advisory services
  • Minimum opening deposit: $25,000

Business Accounts

Business Checking

  • 500 free transactions monthly
  • Cash deposit processing
  • Merchant services integration
  • Business debit cards
  • Online payroll services

Special Accounts

Student Banking

  • No monthly fees for students
  • Free international transfers
  • Educational resources
  • Overdraft protection
  • Student-exclusive rewards

Account Benefits

Security

  • 24/7 fraud monitoring
  • Secure online banking
  • Zero liability protection

Digital Banking

  • Mobile check deposit
  • Bill pay services
  • Account alerts

Support

  • 24/7 customer service
  • Financial advisors
  • Online chat support
